commit.title: [dune] [checker] Dune file with all the dependencies for the checker.
commit.message:
[dune] [checker] Dune file with all the dependencies for the checker.

I opted to list them all instead of doing a glob or depending on a
library as I was curious about what the exact dependencies of the new
binary where.

Unfortunately, we have to bump the Dune version and thus the Docker file.
